24    /**
25    * Concrete deserializer factory class that adds full Bean deserializer
26    * construction logic using class introspection.
27    * Note that factories specifically do not implement any form of caching:
28    * aside from configuration they are stateless; caching is implemented
29    * by other components.
30    *<p>
31    * Instances of this class are fully immutable as all configuration is
32    * done by using "fluent factories" (methods that construct new factory
33    * instances with different configuration, instead of modifying instance).
34    */
